<div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h1 class="font-bebas text-5xl text-brew-black mb-8">Our Story</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
      Bold Brew was born from a simple idea: coffee should be as bold as the people who drink it. We’re here to fuel the go-getters, the dreamers, and the hustlers—the ones who never settle. Our mission is to provide an uncompromisingly strong and smooth cold brew that powers you through every late night and early morning, without the trade-offs of traditional coffee.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div class="flex justify-center">
      <%= image_tag 'tall-glass.jpg', alt: 'Bold Brew Coffee', class: 'rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl w-full max-w-md' %>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center text-center md:text-left">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brew-dark mb-4">Brewing With Integrity</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        We believe that great coffee starts with a great process. We meticulously select our beans from ethical farms and craft our cold brew using a unique, long-period brewing method. This process isn't just about making coffee; it's about unlocking the full, rich potential of every bean, resulting in a brew that’s 70% less acidic and naturally higher in caffeine. It’s the kind of bold flavor that speaks for itself.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mt-16">
    <div class="flex justify-center md:order-2">
      <%= image_tag 'beans-bowl.jpg', alt: 'Our Coffee Beans', class: 'rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl w-full max-w-md' %>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center text-center md:text-left md:order-1">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brew-dark mb-4">A Commitment to Quality</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600">
        From our farms to your cup, every step is a commitment to quality. We don’t just sell coffee; we provide a tool for your success. Our brew is a testament to the hard work and passion that goes into every batch, a promise that we’ll always be here to fuel your drive and help you make your mark on the world. This is where boldness happens.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>